@NODE History "CxBar/Programhistory"
@{LINDENT 3}
@{b}Release 1.7 (30.05.97):@{ub}
  Revision 37.23  1997/05/30 21:20:10
    New: Rexx/Update -> to manually update the rexx menu
         (cause file-deletes in a dir aren't supported by notifying
         of the amiga filesystem FFS, AFS does this!)
    Cat: menuRexxUpdate

  Revision 37.22  1997/05/17 19:33:10
    Chg: If a rexx-script returns a string, CxBar will display only the
         string and won't handle it as an rexx-error.
    New: The rexx-menu updates itself if you add a file to Rexx:CxBar/!
         Deletes aren't recognized by the OS or FileSystem (?)

@{b}Release 1.6 (14.05.97):@{ub}
  Revision 37.21  1997/05/14 18:57:21
    New: All files in "Rexx:CxBar/" will appear (sorted) as a menuitem.
         So you can execute arexx-scripts from CxBar's menu!
    New: The menus are handled within a hook not in the main loop!
    New: RexxCommand "Cx" returns a resultstring (in RESULT) if a name
         couldn't be found!
    Cat: Reorganized the catalog description and added some strings.

@{b}Release 1.51 (26.04.97):@{ub}
  Revision 37.20  1997/04/26 21:09:04
    Fix: If "Menu/Options/Toggle Activity" is on, then "toggle" acts like "enable".

@{b}Release 1.5 (22.04.97):@{ub}
  Revision 37.19  1997/04/22 19:36:17
    New: ARexxCommand: CxGet NAME,TITLE/S,DESCR/S,ENTRIES/S

  Revision 37.18  1997/04/18 19:15:26
    Fix: The (custom) drag- and sizegadgets were sometimes drawn as
         if the window is active, if CxBar just started.

  Revision 37.17  1997/04/12 23:23:10
    Chg: Menu/Options/WindowPos turns to Menu/Window/Position
    New: Menu/Options/Toggle State?
         Do you want to "toggle" state of activity or "enable/disable"?

@{b}Release 1.4 (19.02.97):@{ub}
  Revision 37.16  1997/02/19 20:52:36
    New: HELP opens the AmigaGuide-Help.

  Revision 37.15  1997/02/18 15:37:59
    Fix: Fixed a typo in RegisterText: This is an unregistered...
    New: menu/options/(Un)Snapshot to (un)snapshot the windows position and size.
    Fix: The virtual frame is now configurable.
    Chg: The Register-Reminder-Requester won't come up that often;-)
    Chg: If you start CxBar, when CxBar is already started the second CxBar will
         wait 2 seconds instead 1 second for the first CxBar to quit.

@{b}Release 1.3 (30.09.96):@{ub}
  Revision 37.14  1996/09/30 16:00:20
    New: Localizied strings.
    Arc: Included my Product-Info viewer "VPI", if you don't have it!
    Arc: Made the icons usable;-)

@{b}Release 1.2 (22.09.96):@{ub}
  Revision 37.13  1996/09/21 18:47:49
    Fix: Changed "Releas" in the About-Req. to "Release"
    Fix: SingleTask set to TRUE, so the MUI-Name of CxBar isn't CXBAR.1 anymore.
         It is now CXBAR.
    New: A ARexx-Command (CX) to control the commodities via arexx!
    New: A ARexx-Command (CxList) to get a list of the commodities via arexx!
    Chg: Replaced the command "toggle" by "enable" and "disable".

@{b}Release 1.1:@{ub}
  Revision 37.11  1996/08/10 21:59:42
    Fix: Set aInner(Left|Right|Top|Bottom) of the own drag/size gads to 0.
    Chg: The window doesn't closes&reopened if the Scrollbar should dissappear.
    Chg: The width of the drag&size gadget is a little bit smaller.
    Chg: Name of Menu-Settings "Move&Size window" to "Set window pos."
    New: Added Menu: Settings/Move Window to the/left.
        (here should start v37.12, but I forgot the CheckIn;-(
    New: Menu/Options/Move&Size window -> add intuition drag-/sizegadgets and border.
    New: Menu/Options/Window position/Top,Bottom,Right -> Move the window to the ...
    Chg: During creating/updating the buttons (eg. a new cx added) the application is
         put to sleep, I hope this will fix the startup problems.

  Revision 37.10  1996/07/30 17:30:58
    New: Optional Drag- and Size-Gadget!
    New: The window's pos & size can be optionaly remembered.
    New: Switchable between vertical and horizontal buttons.

  Revision 37.9   1996/07/29 13:24:06
    Fix: Now CxBar recognises if you (or a commodity self) change (s)
         the (his) activity (enable/disable).

@{b}Release 1.0:@{ub}
  Revision 37.8  1996/07/20  13:40:48  tig
        Fix: Could crash on startup, if many commodities were started
             while CxBar is started.
        
        Started to use RCS.

  37.7  (16.07.96):
        Chg: Changed hotkey "numpad *" to aControlChar "*"
        Chg: Changed some internal things

  37.6  (15.07.96):
        New: Numpad * for iconify.
        New: Added Keyfile stuff.
        New: Added a scrollbar option, for 2-button-mouse owner.

  37.5  (08.07.96):
        Chg: internal changes, extracted CxClass to own module
        New: Menu/Options/Iconify Gadget?
        New: Menu/Options/Use|Save
        New: If a cx is inactive, it will be displayed italic else normal

  37.4  (05.07.96):
        Fix: On startup, some CxLstChgs wasn't received.

  37.3  (02.07.96):
        New: Added CycleChain.
        Fix: Finally fixed problems with aShortHelp.
        New: Kill a running 'Exchange', if present at startup.
        New: If brokerList changes the virtGroup doesn't 'jumps' to left
        Now, it works like it should!

  37.2  (01.07.96):
        Chg: Change the buttons from TextSubclass to CycleSubclass.
        Chg: Removed ContextMenus, choose commands from the Cycles.

  37.1  (30.06.96):
        New: Added ContextMenus to call the brokercommands (show,hide..)

  37.0  (29.06.96):
        New: First try, not fully functional.

@{b}@{u}Abbreviations:@{uu}@{ub}

